OL,3,CBritish Transport Police use drones to
OL,4,Ctackle rise in trespassing on tracks
OL,6,FDrones are being used to tackle
OL,7,Ftrespassing on rail tracks, as Network
OL,8,FRail says incidents are on the rise.
OL,10,FLast year on the rail network in
OL,11,FSussex, 24 people lost their lives in
OL,12,Fpreventable accidents. Five of them at
OL,13,Flevel crossings and the rest with
OL,14,Fpeople crossing the line at
OL,15,Funauthorised locations.
OL,17,FDozens of drones are being used across
OL,18,Fthe network, they are armed with night
OL,19,Fvision cameras and heat sensors.
