OL,3,CBritish Transport Police use drones to
OL,4,Ctackle rise in trespassing on tracks
OL,6,FWith the new technology being deployed
OL,7,Fby British Transport Police, officers
OL,8,Fcan more quickly identify the problem
OL,9,Fand how to fix it.
OL,11,FInsp Paul Donovan, British Transport
OL,12,FPolice said: "People take shortcuts.
OL,13,FPeople are attracted to the railway
OL,14,Ffor other reasons. Of course, we do
OL,15,Fhave vulnerable people, who do come
OL,16,Fonto the railway.
