OL,6,F"There's a range of incidents and,
OL,7,Fthat's why (drones) are so good,
OL,8,Fbecause we can find people hiding. We
OL,9,Fcan find people that are at risk to
OL,10,Fthemselves.
OL,12,F"The fantastic thing about the drones
OL,13,Fare they aid our situational awareness
OL,14,Fso we can respond to disruption type
OL,15,Fincidents, and it can aid our decision-
OL,16,Fmaking and help us, in fact minimise
OL,17,Frisks, maximise safety, return to
OL,18,Fnormality as quickly as possible.
OL,20,F"They can get to parts of the line
OL,21,Fthat you can't get to easily.
